For each request the body will write like this:
JSON - {
            "name" : "the name",
            "phoneNumber" : "the number"
       }

please note that the key is unique.

for GET request -
localhost:8080/contacts or localhost:8080/contacts/phoneNumber

for POST request -
localhost:8080/contacts , don't forget to add body

for PUT request -
localhost:8080/contacts/phoneNumber , don't forget to add body

for DELETE request -
localhost:8080/contacts/phoneNumber